I couldn’t control the thieves in Rome, and I couldn’t go back and change what had happened.
What do you gain by being anxious over something you don’t control?
But it is the mark of a wise person to realize that things don’t always go the way we wish.
But there are plenty of ways you can choose to show your love to your partner—and that is under your control.
It is outside of your control (unless you’re Vladimir Putin!)